om/uploads/2023/05/A47E4A5B-34C1-41D7-A25B-DAD581CD.png?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/A47E4A5B-34C1-41D7-A25B-DAD581CD.png?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/A47E4A5B-34C1-41D7-A25B-DAD581CD.png?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/E0CC74D0-168F-4973-9DAE-6B4BCEB7.png?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?w=1500&amp;quality=75 1500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/7AF5E804-E46E-4A59-8C1E-8A5981FE.png?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.toastteathreads.com/summercaps\" target=\"_blank\">Toast Tea Threads Sunhats</a> $60</h3>\n<p>A good sunhat keeps harmful UV rays off your neck, ears, and face. Santa Barbara’s Toast Tea Threads has just the caps to top off your sunny days both on and off the bike with these linen sunhats. Designed to fit under a helmet, they’ll keep you from burning and help keep skin cancer away.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Feather Light</li>\n<li>Foam Brim Stiffener</li>\n<li>Neck flap</li>\n<li>Adjustable Strap</li>\n<li>Sizing:</li>\n<li>Small/Medium: 52-57cm</li>\n<li>Large: 57-63cm</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.toastteathreads.com/summercaps\" target=\"_blank\">Toast Tea Threads</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1300\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?w=1300&amp;quality=75 1300w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/51558850784_b7cb6a3bbd_o_098c43b.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1300\" height=\"1300\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?w=1300&amp;quality=75 1300w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?resize=1024,1024&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/52705025318_d538319c6d_o_d647e0e.png?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.tenkararodco.com/products/tenkaraxtopo?_kx=4huJercNT-Qlw5gGuJ67lsPNjE-omAp3o14bngaeYyc%3D.P4FGZx\" target=\"_blank\">Topo Designs x Tenkara Rod Co</a> $250</h3>\n<p>Simple functionality was the guiding principle used when creating the Topo Designs x Tenkara Rod Co product collaboration. The two brands harnessed their mutual love for getting people outdoors and developed a kit that gives both the new and established Tenkara fisherman everything he/she needs in a small, lightweight package.</p>\n<p><strong>The Topo Designs x Tenkara Rod Co kit includes everything you need to fish:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>From Tenkara Rod Co.</strong> – 10.5 ft medium action Tenkara Rod (The Sierra), Rod Tube, Rod Sock, 10.5 ft. furled Tenkara line, wood line holder, 3 hand tied Tenkara flies, and 1 spool of 5x tippet.</p>\n<p><strong>From TOPO Designs</strong> – Minimalist fishing bag and line wallet.</p>\n<p><b>ROD: </b>This rod is based on Tenkara’s popular Sierra rod model.  Fishing is supposed to be fun, and this rod was developed as its small to medium-sized Tenkara rod. Great for fishing streams, creeks, smaller rivers, ponds, and lakes. And even though it’s not the biggest Tenkara rod it can still handle the occasional bigger fish. Lifetime warranty through Tenkara Rod Co.</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.tenkararodco.com/products/tenkaraxtopo?_kx=4huJercNT-Qlw5gGuJ67lsPNjE-omAp3o14bngaeYyc%3D.P4FGZx\" target=\"_blank\">Tenkara Rod Co</a>.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/2019_Navy_bibshorts_1_2048x2048.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/05/2019_Navy_bibshorts_1_2048x2048.jpg?w=1200